  dialogue:
  - '*picks nose*'
  - Welcome to the Merchant Town, Ninja of Greed.
  - 'The name''s Nickel Nouman. I love money, just like my daddy, THE MERCHANT KING.'
  - 'He told me to tell you "all who wish to visit him must utter his true name".'
  - Whatever that means.
  - Apparently he also has the packet you need to deliver to the king.
  - Solve this riddle - what is the first name of King Modi?
  - That's right! My big daddy will see you now!
  - You're even dumber than I thought! HAHA!
  - You're even dumber than I thought! HAHA!
  - You're even dumber than I thought! HAHA!
